<body><page page_number="1" transcanno_page_id="21"><paragraph class="medium-paragraph" tagcode="1591286127702"><div>Der Kluge Kind<tran_emphasis_id11 class="medium-tran_emphasis_id11" tagcode="1591286079599">!</tran_emphasis_id11></div></paragraph><paragraph class="medium-paragraph" tagcode="1591286127703"><div>Ko*ers Haus <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="war" tagcode="1559055095186">var</orth_error_id12> in <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Flammen" tagcode="1542504180816">flammen</orth_error_id12> geraten. Jans <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Papa" tagcode="1542504244318">Pappa</orth_error_id12> nahm von Haus</div><div>heraus: das Schaukelpferd, ein <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Ball" tagcode="1542504253802">ball</orth_error_id12> und Jans Schultasche, und Jan <tran_word_insertion_id9 class="medium-tran_word_insertion_id9" tagcode="1559055117920">nahm</tran_word_insertion_id9>: <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Papas" tagcode="1542504261694">Pappas</orth_error_id12></div><div>Hut und <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Papas" tagcode="1542504267798">Pappas </orth_error_id12><orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Pfeife" tagcode="1542504273320">pfeife</orth_error_id12>. <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Papa" tagcode="1542504281482">Pappa</orth_error_id12> <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="rannte" tagcode="1542504287352">rante</orth_error_id12> so schnell er <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="konnte" tagcode="1542504296926">konte</orth_error_id12> wieder ins <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Haus" tagcode="1559055148513">haus</orth_error_id12></div><div>um weitere <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Sachen" tagcode="1542504304339">sachen</orth_error_id12> zu retten. Jan nahm die <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Hefte" tagcode="1542504313346">hefte</orth_error_id12> aus die <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Schultasche" tagcode="1559055168647">Schuhltasche</orth_error_id12>,</div><div>er rannte zum <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="flammenspuckende" tagcode="1542504333850">Flammenspukende</orth_error_id12> Fenster und warf die Hefte</div><div>hinein. <orth_error_id12 class="medium-orth_error_id12" orth_error_target="Papa" tagcode="1542504340063">Pappa</orth_error_id12> rannte hinaus und sah ihn. Sie hatten viele Sachen</div><div>gerettet nur das Haus nicht "und die Hefte"<tran_emphasis_id11 class="medium-tran_emphasis_id11" tagcode="1591286097229">!</tran_emphasis_id11></div></paragraph><paragraph class="medium-paragraph" tagcode="1591286127705"><div>Ende<tran_emphasis_id11 class="medium-tran_emphasis_id11" tagcode="1591286127701">!</tran_emphasis_id11></div></paragraph></page></body>
